{"tid":1648823,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]有效文宣方程式:激起情緒->引導->行動呼籲","createTime":"2019-10-12T11:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T00:26:58.000Z","uid":50904,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b413424eb1c762ff945d28d06b783e42152c0d5d","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"原post開係政事台推唔起，重開係創意台希望多啲文宣手足睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加文宣有好多設計人幫手整到好靚，如果背後嘅目標受眾、理念、同目標再針對性啲就可有更大效果。文宣唔單係為左令文字變圖、亦唔係純粹提供資訊，而係一種marketing，用以推銷人地參與活動、甚至拉攏中立者等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過公道啲講，好多時活動發起人、比idea想有人出圖嘅人本身都未必有諗清楚，其實又唔可以怪文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>去到最簡化黎講文宣最好包含三個原素: 激起情緒-&gt;引導-&gt;行動呼籲</strong></span><br />\n以下用點樣令更多加多同路人參與抗爭為例:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQXzVR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQXzVR5.jpg&h=11559325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>呢位義士嘅相，係之前呼籲8/5三罷果陣影</strong></span><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>情緒</strong></span>:傷心/感動/內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>引導</strong></span>:你應該要以罷工黎支持前線手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>行動</strong></span>:參與罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>引用另一位巴打嘅reply，如果想用(偽)中立同藍絲做受眾:</strong></span><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">其實呢個對(偽)中立同藍絲冇效，因為佢哋唔會覺得「傷心/感動/內疚」\n，反而會覺得「冇人叫你幫我擋子彈/抵死/衝出嚟柒」等涼薄嘅評語\n如果理想啲會係「你以為淨係前線示威者先會中子彈? \n喺呢個黑暗時代，下個可能就係你哋呢班無辜市民!!」\n然後細字解釋警察如何濫暴濫捕濫權...\n先有共鳴，再掀動情緒，然後引導，最後行動...</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>大家經常整好多關於警暴嘅文宣，但係無引導讀者嘅情緒、更加無提供對抗/解決嘅行動，結果其實係反而幫手令黑警嘅武力震懾更成功</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O75mC1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO75mC1c.jpg&h=3df049e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>好似我屋企人咁，佢每次睇完到大家傳啲黑警嘅片嘅反應係:</strong></span><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>情緒</strong></span>:嬲、啲差佬無人性架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>自然反</strong>應</span>:怕、好危險架所以你千期唔好參加呢啲遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-&gt;<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>行動</strong></span>:唔好參加、唔好硬碰、心中支持但身體很實誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>大家不妨參考下第一、二次世界大戰嘅propaganda art，佢地係用好多心理學嘅方式挑起你嘅情緒、好有指向性，直頭好似同你1on1對話咁</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如下邊我將佢同啲現有文宣圖mix埋個感覺已經好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呼籲全民抗爭</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWVUVZF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWVUVZF.png&h=347039f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>建立黃色經濟圈</strong></div></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P8O0sL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5P8O0sL.jpg&h=fb3bae29&s={SIZE}\" />    <br />\nbtw,叫人down app如果加埋QR code更好，你睇大公報寫勒索信會教埋你點買bitcoin<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人反抗/打狗救人</span></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QpZyses.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpZyses.jpg&h=2f3850af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依加最少係呢種關於反抗精神/加入街頭抗爭/黑警唔係無敵嘅文宣，其實想搵之前前線手足打到黑警一仆一碌嘅cap圖、但唔記得左用咩keyword，不過岳義精神我諗都唔算離題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便再推一次自己嘅舊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[終極攻略]點樣做會贏? 一齊學習戰爭同戰略</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1599005/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1599005/</a>"},{"pid":"47a0b1d2780cae9ca57d423fa417d3069669fd76","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:27:00.000Z","msg":"Propaganda中文叫政治宣傳，因為呢樣野做得最成功嘅係二戰嘅德國，所以Propaganda呢個字通常帶有洗腦/思想操縱等等嘅負面評價，但我引用返下邊youtube片嘅講法:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;...propaganda as a tool is no more moral or immoral than a pump handle.&quot; - Harold Lasswell<br />\nMorality enters the picture when one judges the ends for which propaganda is used<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">Introduction to Propaganda</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-WpFzTplp28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-WpFzTplp28&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=90e6baae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-WpFzTplp28</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Propaganda During World War 1</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3t_Gwo3M-uc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3t_Gwo3M-uc&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=6e9a623c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3t_Gwo3M-uc</a><br />\n<br />\n順便再推一次自己嘅舊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>[終極攻略]點樣做會贏? 一齊學習戰爭同戰略</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1599005/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1599005/</a>"},{"pid":"8535b0e0aae74684a4012cc2ead6794fd306df66","tid":1648823,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"一句野解釋晒點解場運動會輸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648803</a>"},{"pid":"ab4d928a37756ac06c51278bc1e91f3476499d69","tid":1648823,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0591eef6b728d493521b704f32df53378744c23d","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"自推五連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24490c39880eb0f98261631f5ad33d40e4041a35","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b885f8de326cd206025ad828f8fe6ba3e365d63c","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f201b42bd6ac2e5375b3887eb41e721a3ffb6d0","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870f816f001c1bb072e42e33c475191747c1064","tid":1648823,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b241bdac361705b704e2481a00c0ded2c575c560","tid":1648823,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d555d2091ed2512f027e1273582afc5d871b6ec","tid":1648823,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"高質 推唔到都幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5de938cb239966461047492992add0bef35153","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"希望有文宣組手足睇到嘅話，可以係TG group內叫人黎一齊傾下你地點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4104f0381928c3d80d95da937ecacfb6e2a5cff8","tid":1648823,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"高質文，要重推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23d3716305907b3a9c85e03d1edcceb0d60b5a7","tid":1648823,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d126153b0f4a60c9b55e2b9c13ae54164f39c6fe","tid":1648823,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c511fd0d69b2547fd67150dede931147047440f","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79be1f8f5924d53c0dad803e01d2d214549c1ea4","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d8db9e1b352c6a015aa9d858147c0e14ef4497","tid":1648823,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"1af7289f960d78db99126f5d26802df1d9d60fa0","tid":1648823,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"This is my fight too<br />\n哩張poster好似可以用埋落我地到"},{"pid":"daf489b462b8554e3b4082665fabb0584b3a0ae1","tid":1648823,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:55:14.000Z","msg":"有用post推"},{"pid":"93d762c2cfbcbe4412577f533a6f738993aaee8b","tid":1648823,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:59:02.000Z","msg":"覺得活動好亂既人入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a7acc435567f593cc078cc0111267d8fd49ec219","tid":1648823,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd933a8de4e0dd49d8b5957cace47918d091e90","tid":1648823,"uid":175870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2430ec85af70d35fc9c9018f6724540c6264188","tid":1648823,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468290e335e6615c180460da1faacacc704fc8f5","tid":1648823,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b53650c6a72f63fc491abce644140a9a539900f"